#### How_to_ask_a_nice_question

Before you start to go, you must learn how to ask questions because you will encounter many of questions ranging from daily problems and research ones.

You used to be searching answer on Google.com but it is not always works. Then what you should do next?

>To ask a question, your aim is to get you answer, not to joke someone or greeting them.

Keep in mind just one thing-------To Get the Right Answer.

To get the right answer, you must firstly get the right person.
Sometimes even you get the right person, they may currently have no available answer by hand. They may focus on their own work and don't want ot be bothered.

Then you must find a polite way to approach them, and to statement you problem as clear as you can, let them to help.

And also...wait, I got to go.....
